# Compressors

It has been stated earlier that a simple cycle gas turbine consists of a compression process, a heat addition process and an expansion process. Various devices are required to achieve these processes.
Q: Who authored the work on the fuel cell/gas turbine hybrid system mentioned in the text?
A: Samuelsen, S. is credited as the author, representing the National Fuel Cell Research Centre, University of California, Irvine.
